set name=pkg.description value="GlassFish JTS package provides XA transaction support. For more information on Java Transaction Service (JTS), please refer to http://java.sun.com/javaee/technologies/jts/. GlassFish v3 is an application server created using modular, lightweight, extensible architecture built on OSGi.  It is the first implementation of Java EE 6 standard and is a great developer platform, starts fast, is easy to use and has extensions to support dynamic languages like jRuby."
